Life-History Schedule

Source: R/schedule.R
ypr_schedule.Rd

Generates a tibble of the life-history schedule by age for a population.

ypr_schedule(population, complete = FALSE, check = TRUE)

Arguments

population

A list of population life-history parameters.
complete

A flag indicating whether to generate a complete schedule.
check

A flag indicating whether to check the arguments.

Value

A tibble of the life-history schedule by age.

See also

ypr_population and plot.ypr_population.

Examples

ypr_schedule(ypr_population())
